## Deployments module

- **`internal/modules/deployments/`** — `GET /api/v1/deployments/list|timeline|impact|active-version` (query `serviceName`, range `start`/`end`); **`registry.Cached`** (30s). Uses **`observability.spans`** with `mat_service_version` / `mat_deployment_environment` materialized columns.

## Service Topology module

- **`internal/modules/services/topology/`** — `GET /api/v1/services/topology` (range `startMs`/`endMs`, optional `?service=<name>` for 1-hop neighborhood). Returns `{nodes, edges}` with RED metrics per service and per edge. Nodes aggregate inbound spans (`kind_string IN ('SERVER','CONSUMER')`); edges are parent→child span joins. `registry.Cached` (30s). Health thresholds: errorRate >5% unhealthy, >1% degraded.

